originalText.text: Dr Cynthia Keh and her dental assistant Vicky have paid more attention to detail than any other dentist I have gone to, complete with a great sense of humor and patience. She created an individualized treatment plan for me, providing instructions on how to care for my teeth and gums and what to look out for. Dr Keh’s office is also so easy to communicate with - whether by phone, email or texting. And a wonderful location - Central Park south with a lovely clinic, also open on Saturdays! I highly recommend Dr Keh, especially for us healthcare professionals

originalText.text: Very good experience with Dr. Keh! First thing first, the office is nice and clean and the staffs are friendly and helpful. Dr. Keh has great bedside manners and really gave me a detailed and comprehensive dental exam which is exactly what I need. Highly recommend Dr. Keh to anyone that needs dental care and are looking for a healthy smile.
